{"tid":2373617,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【影片】卸任大律師公會主席　戴啟思：司法不再完全獨立","createTime":"2021-01-20T14:44:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T03:39:19.000Z","uid":240362,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1918a3094bf0d3d61cda693493670314a9a3610d","tid":2373617,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T14:44:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/704667913560155\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F704667913560155&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia5hvY2R4XAiH6OvuWOSnKsk%3D&h=ae1880d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/704667913560155</a><br />\n<br />\n大律師公會明天（21 日）換屆，跟據會章，67 歲的資深大律師戴啟思須於今年卸任。1984 年戴啟思從英國來港，半生關注人權議題，港區國安法成了戴啟思任內最後、也是最大的一場挑戰。他說「我們不再有個完全獨立的司法制度」。<br />\n<br />\n2019、2020 年過後，街頭動盪平息，戴啟思指平靜街頭才是問題所在，「如果『平靜』的代價是禁止所有政治表達的形式，這只是猶如墳場裡的平靜（peace of the graveyard），不會是我們希望在社會見到的平靜。一個健康的社會，是需要政治辯論和反對聲音的。」<br />\n<br />\n專訪全文：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3bSWMLr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3bSWMLr&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia5hvY2R4XAiH6OvuWOSnKsk%3D&h=ca5920ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3bSWMLr</a>"},{"pid":"ec36bddeeec74026d0a065a71f5323e301ebfc83","tid":2373617,"uid":20867,"like":6,"dislike":19,"score":-13,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T14:48:28.000Z","msg":"我認為每一位中文科教師都應該能夠指出<br />\n<br />\n點解「司法不再完全獨立」系一句病句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f22bef4fea925c706f872c82e3ba8fdee98b77","tid":2373617,"uid":304769,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"ec36bddeeec74026d0a065a71f5323e301ebfc83","tid":2373617,"uid":20867,"like":6,"dislike":19,"score":-13,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T14:48:28.000Z","msg":"我認為每一位中文科教師都應該能夠指出<br />\n<br />\n點解「司法不再完全獨立」系一句病句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T14:49:31.000Z","msg":"